.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, tram, ship
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cycling, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the fan of trance is between the person drinking almond-milk and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk | fanta     | cola       |
| Transport          | snowmobile   | ship    | tram | quad-bike       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
| Sport         | cycling  | ice-hockey  | badminton | basketball |

