 8. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
