.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, sudoku, video-games
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, kiwi, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, metal, r&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, skateboard, van
 1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person driving the van is the fan of r&b##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
11. the person eating strawberry is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess      | video-games | sudoku       | drawing   |
| Food   | strawberry     | carrot | kiwi | broccoli |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | dubstep     | metal        | r&b       |
| Transport     | skateboard | motorbike   | helicopter   | van       |

